NAME

JSON::Pointer::Marpa - Marpa::R2 based JSON Pointer RFC 6901 implementation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module manually, run the following commands:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

DOCUMENTATION

After the installation, you can find further documentation using the commands:

  perldoc JSON::Pointer::Marpa

MAINTENANCE

To maintain this module, run the following commands:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make PERL_CPANM_OPT="--notest --with-develop --with-recommends" installdeps 
  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make RELEASE_TESTING=1 test  # use Test::Harness
  make RELEASE_TESTING=1 testp # use TAP::Harness
  make cover

The second command installs the module dependencies in a "local" directory
using "cpanm".

